                    <b>design and the look of the brand.</b> Another major
                    problem was that the
                    <b
                      >API which I have used does not have a lot of
                      documentation.</b
                    >
                    I got stuck on a lot of
                    <b>CORS and proxy related issues</b> and it took me a few
                    days just to properly get the implementation of the API. In
                    this project I encountered a lot of difficulties for the
                    first time but I managed to overcome them and provide a
                    beautifully designed user-experience.
                  </p>
